
Simple C program to read Gadget snapshots and output basic information.

Usage:

readsnap <filename> <[option]>

options
-------
 -info   prints byte information for all fields present
 -h      only the header information is printed to the screen
 -m      prints the mass of a particle when displaying other information
 -id     prints the ID for each particle.
 -pot    prints the Potential for every particle.
 -tm     prints the total mass of each type
 -gm     prints the gas mass


If no options are set, it will print basic snap information to a file, ic.txt.


